Class GenerateCSV

Object
GenerateCSV
All Implemented Interfaces:
Generate
public class GenerateCSV extends Object implements Generate
The GenerateCSV class provides methods to generate various reports in CSV format for a camp management system. It includes methods for generating reports filtered by attendee, camp committee member, no filter, and performance.
Author:
Gao Linyue
